# Mapa web
m <- leaflet() %>% 
  addProviderTiles(providers$Esri.WorldImagery, group = "Imgenes de ESRI") %>% 
  addProviderTiles(providers$Stamen.TonerLite, group = "Stamen Toner Lite") %>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$OpenStreetMap.Mapnik, group = "OpenStreetMap") %>%
  addCircleMarkers(data = Lapa_verde,
                   stroke = F,
                   radius = 4,
                   fillColor = 'green',
                   fillOpacity = 1,
                   group = "Lapa Verde",
                   popup = paste(Lapa_verde$locality, 
                                 Lapa_verde$year, 
                                 sep = '<br/>'
                   )
  ) %>%
  addCircleMarkers(data = Quetzal,
                   stroke = F,
                   radius = 4,
                   fillColor = 'Black',
                   fillOpacity = 1,
                   group = "Quetzal",
                   popup = paste(Quetzal$locality, 
                                 Quetzal$year, 
                                 sep = '<br/>'
                   )
  ) %>%
  addRasterImage(cr_altitud, 
                 colors = pal, 
                 opacity = 0.8, 
                 group = "Altitud"
                 
  ) %>%
  addRasterImage(cr_bio$bio12_23, 
                 colors = palp, 
                 opacity = 0.8, 
                 group = "Precipitacion"
  ) %>%
  addLayersControl(
    baseGroups = c("OpenStreetMap", "Stamen Toner Lite", "Imgenes de ESRI"),
    overlayGroups = c("Altitud", "Precipitacion","Lapa Verde","Quetzal"),
    options = layersControlOptions(collapsed = FALSE)    
  ) %>%
  addLegend(pal = pal, 
            values = values(cr_altitud), 
            title = "Altitud"
  ) %>%
  addLegend(pal = palp, 
            values = values(cr_bio$bio12_23),
            position = "topleft" ,
            title = "Precipitacion"
  ) %>%
  addMiniMap(
    toggleDisplay = TRUE,
    position = "bottomleft",
    tiles = providers$Stamen.TonerLite
  )

m

```
